---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Shipping Policy | Complete Health Peptides"
  description="Learn about our shipping methods, timeframes, costs, and delivery information for domestic and international orders."
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-secondary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Shipping Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Information about our shipping methods, delivery timeframes, and costs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Shipping Information</h2>
        <p>At Complete Health Peptides, we strive to ship all orders promptly and securely. Below you'll find information about our shipping policies and procedures.</p>
        
        <h3>Processing Times</h3>
        <p>Most orders are processed within 1-2 business days. Orders placed before 2:00 PM EST on business days are typically processed the same day. Orders placed after 2:00 PM EST or on weekends/holidays will be processed the next business day.</p>
        
        <h3>Shipping Methods & Timeframes</h3>
        
        <div class="overflow-x-auto my-6">
          <table class="min-w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300">
            <thead>
              <tr class="bg-gray-100">
                <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Shipping Method</th>
                <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Estimated Delivery Time</th>
                <th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Cost</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Standard Shipping (US)</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">3-5 business days</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Free on orders over $100<br>$10 for orders under $100</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Express Shipping (US)</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">1-2 business days</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">$25</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">International Shipping</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">7-14 business days</td>
                <td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Calculated at checkout<br>(based on weight and destination)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Tracking Information</h3>
        <p>Once your order ships, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with tracking information. You can also track your order by logging into your account on our website.</p>
        
        <h3>International Shipping</h3>
        <p>We ship to most international destinations. Please note that international customers are responsible for all duties, import taxes, and any other fees that may be imposed by their country. These fees are not included in the shipping cost and will be collected upon delivery.</p>
        
        <h3>Cold Shipping & Temperature Control</h3>
        <p>For temperature-sensitive products, we offer cold shipping options with specialized packaging to maintain product integrity. There may be additional charges for cold shipping, which will be indicated during checkout.</p>
        
        <h3>Delivery Issues</h3>
        <p>If your package is returned to us due to an incorrect address, refused delivery, or failure to pick up, you will be responsible for the cost of reshipping. If you believe your package is lost or damaged, please contact our customer service team within 7 days of the expected delivery date.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-primary-50 border-l-4 border-primary-500 p-4 my-6">
          <h4 class="text-primary-700 font-bold">Have questions about shipping?</h4>
          <p class="text-primary-700">Contact our customer service team at <a href="mailto:support@completehealthpeptides.com" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">support@completehealthpeptides.com</a> or call us at 1-800-555-1234.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>